name: Hundred GO
description:
Hundred GO is shooter, action-adventure game.

You called Meatsaver, you have to complete the game and save your meat.

You will face some monsters like Davi, Mushroo Man, Hog Rider, Skele slime and more.

you need to spend the 100 keys wisely.

The game made for Android.

Requirements: 2GB RAM

                                  500MB ROM

                                  ANDROID 8 or above
